  Source:
    Title: The Glory of the World
Tags:
  - Life-Love=The Primordial State=Materia Prima and Human Perfection
---
The fire of the Sages may be extracted from all natural things, and is
called the quintessence. It is of earth, water, air. and fire. It has
no cause of corruption or other contrary quality.
